ith PT Indosiar Karya Mandiri, Tbk. (IKM) being the holding company of PT Indosiar Visual Mandiri (Indosiar), with SCM being the “surviving company.” The merger is set forth in the Deed No. 177 dated 5th April 2013, made before Dr. IrawanSoerodjo, S.H., M.Si., Notary in Jakarta. Furthermore, the amendment of Articles of Association of SCM has been granted approval by the Minister of Laws and Human Rights of the Republic of Indonesia by virtue of the Decree of the Ministry of Laws and Human Rights of Republic of Indonesia No. AHU-21349.AH.01.02.The year 2013 dated 19th April 2013.</p>', '{:en}Company Profile{:}{:id}Profil Perusahaan{:}', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'company-profile', '', '', '2016-01-20 08:58:30', '2016-01-20 08:58:30', '', 16, 'http://localhost/scm/?page_id=150', 0, 'page', '', 0),
